{"tid":579541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Bakerie 真係好正","createTime":"2018-03-03T16:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T16:47:12.000Z","uid":149118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"357069bab0e8c9aeaaca8deb88569cf17df2ba30","tid":579541,"uid":149118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"啱啱開錯台冇乜反應。而家開多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人認為Bakerie 早班火車呢首歌好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然可能冇乜人識佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我覺得大家一定要聽下呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前嚟過我學校表演不過嗰陣時唔識佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次老佛爺香港站我都有去<br />\n我覺得佢哋應該要紅過啲香港嘅主流歌星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6SvD5pA33Ew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6SvD5pA33Ew&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=cf269733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6SvD5pA33Ew</a><br />\n睇埋紀錄片了解下佢地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6nsaz4MoPJA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6nsaz4MoPJA&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=cc27049f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6nsaz4MoPJA</a><br />\n佢哋其他歌都好正 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2uMsrsMeGUE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2uMsrsMeGUE&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=51ad685d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2uMsrsMeGUE</a><br />\n當然仲有刀哥呢首<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VJIM8y9dJNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVJIM8y9dJNs&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6ff0